{
  "stem": "4686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One floor of the flat house was broken slew and separate men's part and the woman strictly, kept away with a wall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had an old, for me, an old rabbi, Rabbi Stern.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was also--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was also my teacher in the elementary school, teaching Jewish things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came to our house many times because also my uncle who lived next door, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bertie ?] was very religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was our synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's where we went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a big yard outside and all the kids, we were just running up and down there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when that became very angry, then he grabbed me and made me sit down between him and [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bertie ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bachi. ?] and that was the High Holy Days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Baroshutso ?] Synagogue, nothing special.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a reasonably large family synagogue, not one of the big built synagogues.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember before Yom Kippur to go out next to us was a big garden like-- like a botanical garden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there where we feeding the fishes before Yom Kippur and the [INAUDIBLE], the chicken, with the chickens and taking it to the butcher to get it cut after.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, my mother was a little lady even then, reasonably well fed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we lived about three houses from the corner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The corner was the bus stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In many cases, my mother took a taxi when she went over to Auntie [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bergie ?] or went into the city because she just couldn't walk because her feet was hurting and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's still hurting thanks goodness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had what we needed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I went to-- to the Jewish high school.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
